
=begin pod
=TITLE Fontawesome plugin for Collection

Plugin provides Fontawesome icons when the C< F<> > FormatCode is encountered in Pod6 content files.

Currently only Fontawesome 4.47 is supported.

The FormatCode has the form C< F<name|other classes> > which render as

    <span class="fa name other classes"></span>

The other classes can be found in the FontAwesome documentation

=end pod